      "oneLiner": "ValCtrl is the world model for Prediction Finance, and Kassandre\u2026",
      "longDescription": "ValCtrl is building the world model for Prediction Finance. Prediction markets contain useful prices about the future, but today those prices are fragmented across venues, titles, rules, and proxy contracts. Users think in beliefs; markets are stored as scattered contracts.\r\n\r\nOur first product is Kassandre Search. Users type a natural-language belief, and Kassandre maps it to relevant prediction markets with backtrace and quality labels. Existing markets are the first scaffold. The long-term product path is search -> composed exposures -> native quotes -> gated bet/trade placement, with legal/compliance gates respected at each step.\r\n\r\nWe are looking for hard belief-to-market queries from forecasters, investors, operators, and YC founders.",
